{"type": "article", "id": 29729, "title": "Swatch预计上半年盈利暴跌，以及日本潮流“教主”NIGO为自家品牌拍广告｜浮华日报", "description": "我们为你挑选了今天最重要和最好看的时尚新闻。", "date": "2016-07-18T03:18:10Z", "super_tag": "", "tags": [{"id": 10, "name": "法国"}, {"id": 50, "name": "日本"}, {"id": 347, "name": "内衣"}, {"id": 393, "name": "收购"}, {"id": 3835, "name": "瑞士"}, {"id": 5442, "name": "钟表"}, {"id": 6863, "name": "纽约男装周"}, {"id": 16969, "name": "暴跌"}, {"id": 25335, "name": "lookbook"}, {"id": 30277, "name": "摇滚乐团"}, {"id": 442, "name": "HUMAN MADE"}, {"id": 2636, "name": "Swatch"}, {"id": 2949, "name": "McQ"}, {"id": 13713, "name": "Raf Simon"}, {"id": 30278, "name": "华歌尔"}, {"id": 30279, "name": "Brunello Cucinelli"}, {"id": 30280, "name": "伯爵"}, {"id": 30281, "name": "赫斯特传媒"}, {"id": 30282, "name": "Huit"}, {"id": 441, "name": "NIGO"}], "category": 19, "column": 8, "author": 113313, "comment_count": 2, "praise_count": 41, "image": "img/article/article_show/20160718102718NXxkeynsC0ioJ5V7.jpg", "contents": "<h3>一些重要的新闻</h3><div><p><a href=\"http://www.forbes.com/sites/robertanaas/2016/07/14/piaget-polo-s-steel-ryan-reynolds-watches-polo/#d8213707091b\" rel=\"nofollow\"><b>伯爵表新推出较低价位的全钢系列</b></a>｜伯爵（Piaget）近日于纽约发布新系列 Piaget Polo S，全钢系列和入门级的价格，面向“千禧一代”，Ryan Reynolds 及 Michael B. Jordan 担任品牌形象大使。以往伯爵表的入门级系列单价在 20000 美元左右，而 Piaget Polo S 的售价约为 9350-12400 美元。</p><p><a href=\"http://wwd.com/business-news/financial/swatch-warns-sales-profits-for-the-first-half-of-10490477/\" rel=\"nofollow\"><b>Swatch 预计上半年盈利大跌</b></a>｜瑞士腕表品牌 Swatch 集团近日在一项计划外声明中宣布，受到消费需求锐减以及香港、法国等地第三方订单取消等因素的影响，预计品牌在前六个月内的销售额将下跌 12%，营业利润及净收入将有 50-60% 的大幅下滑。Swatch 将在 7 月 21 日宣布上半年财政结果。</p><p><a href=\"http://wwd.com/media-news/fashion-memopad/budget-cuts-at-hearst-magazine-industry-advertising-pullback-fall-10491044/\" rel=\"nofollow\"><b>赫斯特传媒或将全面缩紧预算</b></a>｜WWD 最近采访到赫斯特传媒员工，后者表示公司将全面缩减预算开支。据业内人士透露今年晚些还将裁员。集团总裁 David Carey  确认了削减开支的消息，但否认将全面进行。此前 WWD 就报道过 Ralph Lauren 将缩减纸质杂志广告秋季投放预算，不少传统广告主都有削减印刷媒体投放预算趋势、读者也花费更少用于订阅。</p><p><a href=\"http://www.nofashion.cn/a/1468558737410.html\" rel=\"nofollow\"><b>Brunello Cucinelli 上半年收入上涨</b></a>｜意大利奢侈品集团 Brunello Cucinelli 截至 6 月 30 日的上半年收入，从去年同期的 2.003 亿欧元同比增长 9.7% 至 2.198 亿欧元。大中华地区上半年增幅显著，增速从一季度的 11.1% 上升至 15%。</p><p><a href=\"http://m.us.fashionmag.com/news/Huit-officially-acquired-by-Trendy-Capital,714168.html\" rel=\"nofollow\"><b>Trendy Capital&nbsp;收购内衣品牌 Huit</b></a><b></b>｜创立于 1981 年的法国内衣品牌 Huit，2012 曾年由日本集团华歌尔（Wacoal ）收购，更名为Huit8。近日 Huit 宣布被Trendy Capital 收购，并将以“Huit France” 为品牌名称。<br></p></div><h3><span style=\"font-family: inherit; background-color: transparent;\">一些值得一看的：</span></h3><p>Opening Ceremony 推出最新的<a href=\"http://hypebeast.com/2016/7/opening-ceremony-club-usa\" rel=\"nofollow\">夏季胶囊系列 “Club USA”</a>：</p><p class=\"multiple\"></p><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201607180832514R6wiaBPrb7JFLdz.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.667002\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160718083252nQmOX0BPHf5GxLc6.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.667002\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160718083254ybX4QVG7zSBJjEYv.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.667002\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160718083304PSZT6Ne3oynfWiV2.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.667002\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160718083305ZpFci04Qkf5ojIz6.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.667002\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160718083335OX0W5e6oE4LrTPfZ.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.667002\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><p></p><p class=\"\">日本潮流界领军人物 NIGO 为自己的品牌 HUMAN MADE 拍摄了<a href=\"http://hypebeast.com/2016/7/human-made-2016-fall-winter-collection\" rel=\"nofollow\">秋冬新品的 lookbook</a>：<br></p><div class=\"com-insert-images medium-insert-images-wide\"><p></p><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160718083224MU2gWlkO6AtCGQpI.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666992\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160718083225Ldx5Pl2OZnoMVj4z.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666992\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160718083224cCS7QALHzWkaY1tv.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666992\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160718083226gk7BJzO2iCu90AnW.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666992\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160718083224UM9TvQVpoyBEkwW1.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666992\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160718083226gRvhob84Sxwnj03M.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666992\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160718083226qjn67QfKVWydE21u.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666992\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><p class=\"\">美国设计师品牌&nbsp;<a href=\"http://www.fashiongonerogue.com/rebecca-minkoff-shopbop-street-chic/\" rel=\"nofollow\">Rebecca Minkoff 发布春夏系列 lookbook</a>：</p><p class=\"multiple\"></p><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160718095928lqBfLov9MZQ8sTgm.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.761250\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160718095929FIQ8HzP5Lwj2b91K.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.710000\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/2016071809592979w8cSaB54mEWYnj.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.775000\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160718095931f2MI5qHjKLDkNFys.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.776250\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><p></p><p class=\"\">芝加哥潮流店铺 RSVP Gallery 拍摄了<a href=\"http://hypebeast.com/2016/7/raf-simons-2016-fall-winter-editorial-rsvp\" rel=\"nofollow\"> Raf Simons 2016 秋冬系列特辑</a>：<br></p><div class=\"com-insert-images medium-insert-images-wide\"><p></p><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/2016071808341692Jk3WwC68vqz1cA.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666923\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160718083416CQPYso38THgAplZu.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666923\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201607180834182BfoOxWYyvkHRJ84.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666923\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160718083418o8aA2WOcTBnpfkVL.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666923\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160718083419QbqgnUfE4COueKIP.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666923\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201607180834207haAtfU40wsMT1GO.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666923\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><p>意大利机能服装品牌 <a href=\"http://hypebeast.com/2016/7/stone-island-nyc-flagship-location\" rel=\"nofollow\">Stone Island 在纽约开了新旗舰店</a>：</p><p class=\"multiple\"></p><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160718085507e1M6HfcikY0tonFz.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666463\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160718085507ah82GwcJNZ0ExRku.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666463\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160718085508ngQUckRJDxoATqzE.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666463\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160718085508lnrW0eNCtMfw9qs1.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666463\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160718085510XSvQ4UhEj5TuZNmR.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666463\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201607180855126KIisE28hgNtOkmZ.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666463\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><p></p><p class=\"\">Alexander McQueen 姊妹品牌 McQ，找来日本摇滚乐团 Bo Ningen 来<a href=\"http://www.dazeddigital.com/fashion/article/32061/1/harley-weir-captures-japanese-rock-band-for-mcq\" rel=\"nofollow\">拍摄 2016 秋冬季广告大片</a>：<br></p><div class=\"com-insert-images medium-insert-images-wide\"><p></p><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160718100807CgVTabyjQXRNsGK5.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.841111\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160718100807XcTgnsl9CfOeSuU5.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.806667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160718100807SEWdGPomn9MlNshb.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.812222\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/2016071810080875AiNKuLMxgZwWSO.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.810433\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160718100808Jt9VOqSWfNv25DXm.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.808889\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160718100809SLtRXT76MQ3clw4K.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.619922\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160718100810jACP2I9OisSxzaZ5.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.615427\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><p>洛杉矶时尚品牌 <a href=\"http://fashionista.com/2016/07/second-layer-spring-2017\" rel=\"nofollow\">Second/Layer 纽约男装周发布春夏系列</a>，中性的街头风格。此外，品牌刚刚入围国际羊毛标志大奖(Woolmark Prize Award) 决赛。</p><div cl